Package org.restlet.rebind

Class Summary
AnnotationInfo Descriptor for method annotations.
AnnotationUtils Utilities to manipulate Restlet annotations.
ClientProxyGenerator Deferred binding generator capable of creating a subclass of GwtClientProxy implementing a custom Java interface, extending the marker ClientProxy interface, and annotated with Restlet annotations such as Get, Post, Put or Delete.
